reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Stylish work bag
reviews.reviewText: I finally found a nice roomy laptop bag for work. I don't always carry my laptop but when I need to - its perfect. I'm a teacher and mom. The bag fits my planner, books, folder of lesson plans to be copied and my breastpump and nursing cover. It's very sturdy and I love the animal print.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very handsome bag, makes great Christmas gift
reviews.reviewText: This bag is one of the most attractive and sturdiest carry-all bags I've ever seen. I bought it as a Christmas gift for a friend who is always carrying stuff around and I know she'll love it. It's BIG, with ample pockets, and versatile because she can carry it in her hand or over her shoulder. It's actually far more handsome than the pic makes out. It shipped folded up but I unrolled it and stuffed it with tissue so that it would present well as a gift. You'll need a fairly large-sized box if you do it that way, but it's more attractive as a gift if you unroll it. I highly recommend this!

reviews.reviewText: Lightweight, adjustable strap and many pockets - perfect teacher bag!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 30, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This bag is super cute and sturdy. It seems really good quality and roomy for the size. However, there are no pockets which is inconvenient for all the little odds and ends that I normally have in pockets of my purses. It can also get pretty heavy quickly since it has a good amount of weight on its own without any items in it. Overall a good purchase though and will hopefully use for a good while.

reviews.reviewText: I had the same bag for years that crammed everything together.. this bag is perfect size, has a secure cushioned area for my laptop and little zipper pockets for the chargers and paperwork that I throw inside. Plus, it’s cute!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love this bag
reviews.reviewText: I bought this to use as my new teacher bag. I love it so much! It fits a laptop, lunch bag, large water bottle and small pencil/cosmetic and has room to spare. It is durable and well made. I may order some additional straps so I can switch them out.
